::Cygnar::
       He nods solemnly and smiles at the two commanders.  "Perhaps we shall 
succeed yet."  He opens a channel to Cryotek.  "Alright I need you to go to 
these coordinates as fast as you can.  Oh, and bring Rancor with you."  He 
transmits the coordinates of the Tripred base and turns to Tyrael, "We should 
be going now."
